title: LEGO Batman Series
deadline: 21 days remainingZero Budget • For non-profit • Custom audition
script: "Hey there, Bat-friend! Here’s one to tickle your brain: What has a heart that doesn’t beat? Solve it quick, before I make my escape on this wild Gotham street!"
description: One of the Dark Knight's most infamous villains, Edward Nygma, loves showing off his intelligence by committing crimes and leaving clues for Batman. This habit leads to the Riddler's capture and being sent to Arkham Asylum. His genius allows him to create complex traps and use innocent people as bait. He sees them as disposable in his battle against Batman.
